column10: I was riding south on S. Irving St., coming to a stop at the stop sign at 2nd St. S. A driver made a left from 2nd St. S. northbound on S. Irving St. He turned into the wrong side of S. Irving St. (his left) almost hitting me before he swerved right to miss me.
